document_data.Notable Morkoths:
* [[Arxhadk]], the morkoth ambassador of [[Olleth]] in [[Sshamath]], ''circa'' [[1370 DR]].
* [[Gayar]], an ancient and soft-spoken morkoth wizard and member of the [[Dukars]] that lived in the city of Myth Nantar.<ref>
* [[M'warien]], a morkoth that lived in the [[Sea of Swords]] and claimed the [[Eye of Xxiphu (item)|Eye of Xxiphu]] in the late-15{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Mysterious Isle|4}}{{Cite adventurers league/Eye of Xxiphu|4}}  
* [[Sallissi]], a morkoth that lived in the underground [[Nepenthe River]] in the late 14{{th}} century DR.
* [[Vlantir]], an Inner Sea morkoth who was a devout servant of Those Who Sleep Below.{{Cite dungeon/79/The Akriloth|63}}
